rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Did you hear about the ruckus
that happened the other night?

rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently there was some kind of chase.
The military and some mystery individuals,
leaping across the rooftops.

rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard there was some scary stuff
going down in Gula, but I never
dreamed it would happen here.

rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Peace has reigned for a while now,
but maybe times are starting to
take a turn for the worse...

rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0005
rows.name:
At any rate, I don't know how
they managed it, leaping about
such precarious places.

rows.label: tlk45300054_02_msg0006
rows.name:
I'd probably get a heart attack
just thinking about it.
